songs.title: Things Fall Apart
songs.lyrics:
Things fall apart and I guess things fade
I can't change that and I can't stay mad
Still feel your touch when I'm laying in bed
All my friends say that it's all in my head

Things fall apart and I guess things fade
I can't change that and I can't stay mad
All my friends say that it's not that bad
She said "I'll hit you up" but she never called back
